name: Outdoor Kangaroo Lounge Chair
description: Make a Mid Century Modern statement in your outdoor space. The Outdoor Kangaroo Lounge Chair draws inspiration from the iconic Kangaroo chair silhouette. Made of solid teak wood which has been treated to withstand outdoor conditions. Slatted wood details add a textural interest. Style alone or complete the set with the matching Outdoor Coffee Table or Kangaroo Outdoor Sofa.
